metadata.name: TAMED
metadata.description:
AI generated video of a girl tamed in a cold and creepy facility reminding of old school horror movies.

Turn on your sound and get scared.

The video is the first collaboration between L3THO NFTs & SOLW1p3R. More projects will follow.
